abraflexi-cli (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add status command to verify server connection and company state.
  * Add record create operation with mandatory-field validation and --force flag.
  * Add manpage (man/abraflexi-cli.1) covering all commands and options.
  * Add AppStream metainfo (debian/abraflexi-cli.metainfo.xml).
  * Install application icon to /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/.
  * Add PHPUnit command-configuration tests.
  * Add autopkgtest coverage for status, list-companies, and list-evidences.

